HEADWORD: Phrenomagnetism
<hw>Phre`no*mag"net*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>frh`n</grk>, <grk>freno`s</grk>, the mind + E.
